This directory vendors and modifies code from:

  application-loopback
  Copyright (c) 2025 Matin Tat
  Licensed under the MIT License
  https://github.com/WerdoxDev/application-loopback

Modifications by R3dWolfie (2026):
  - Replaced single-mode CLI entrypoint with --include-pid / --exclude-pid flags
    so the helper can capture system audio while EXCLUDING a process tree
    (which is what RedVoice needs to keep its own playback out of the
    screenshare audio mix).
  - Removed the silence-drop optimization in OnAudioSampleRequested so the
    output stream is sample-rate accurate (no gaps when no app is making
    sound), and added fflush(stdout) for low-latency streaming.

